---
title: Chicken Fried Rice with Mushrooms, Sugar Snap Peas and Peanuts
description: This Chicken Fried Rice is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-fried-rice-b331ddcd-13e6ed82.jpg
